		<part id="evolution">
			<title>Landscape Evolution</title>
			<slide id="evolution-levels">
				<title>Evolution: Environments and Solutions</title>
				<ul>
					<li><em>Level 1:</em> Solutions evolve to increase individual fitness</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Solutions are evaluated for fitness based on the environment</li>
						<li>Feedback about solutions helps to increase their fitness</li>
					</ul>
					<li><em>Level 2:</em> Environment changes trigger fitness function changes</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Changes in the environment are outside the control of solutions</li>
						<li>Solution fitness changes without solutions changing</li>
					</ul>
					<li><em>Level 3:</em> Solution spaces change allowing new solutions</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Solutions are given new manoeuvring space</li>
						<li>Fitness functions need to be adjusted accordingly</li>
					</ul>
				</ul>
			</slide>
