		<part id="conclusions">
			<title>Conclusions</title>
			<slide id="why-what-how">
				<title>Continuous Architecting</title>
				<ul>
					<li><em>Why:</em> Explain and review every constraint</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Keeps architecture lean</li>
					</ul>
					<li><em>What:</em> Constrain behavior without assumptions about implementations</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Separates architectural and implementation issues</li>
					</ul>
					<li><em>How:</em> Provide guidance and support for implementing constraints</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Helps teams to do the right thing if they are looking for support</li>
					</ul>
				</ul>
			</slide>
